{
  "chapter": "130",
  "title": "太史公自序",
  "translations": {
    "81": {
      "title": "赵世家",
      "text": "<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">骥</span>与<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">騄耳</span>等良马，是因为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">造父</span>才显名于世。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵夙</span>效忠<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晋献公\">献（晋献公）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵衰</span>续承其业。辅佐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晋文公\">文（晋文公）</span>尊奉周王，终成<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国辅臣。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">襄子</span>受困受辱，终擒<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">智伯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主父</span>被生擒幽禁，饿极而探鸟雀而死。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王迁</span>荒淫邪僻，良将因而见斥。嘉许<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵鞅\">鞅（赵鞅）</span>讨伐<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>室之乱，故作赵<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第十三。"
    },
    "82": {
      "title": "魏世家",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毕万</span>受封<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>地，卜人早已预知其兴。及至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">绛</span>地<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">戮</span>杀栾盈同党，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">戎翟</span>归附。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文侯</span>仰慕仁义，尊<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子夏</span>为师。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦惠王\">惠王（秦惠王）</span>自负骄矜，被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>击。既而猜疑<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">信陵</span>君，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>遂与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>绝交。终至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span>陷落，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王假</span>沦为俘虏。嘉许<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏武子\">武（魏武子）</span>辅佐<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晋文公\">文（晋文公）</span>伸张<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">霸道</span>，故作魏<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第十四。"
    },
    "83": {
      "title": "韩世家",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩厥</span>暗中施<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">阴德</span>保全赵氏孤儿，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵武</span>因此兴复。续绝世、立废君，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国人都尊奉他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭侯</span>列于贤君之名，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申子</span>为其所用。猜疑贤士而不能任信，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>人乘机<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">袭</span>击。嘉许他们辅佐<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国、匡扶<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>之事，故作韩<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第十五。"
    },
    "84": {
      "title": "田敬仲完世家",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">完子</span>避难，奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>寻求依托，暗施恩德于<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五世</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人为其歌颂。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成子</span>得掌政权，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田和</span>终立为诸侯。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王建</span>动心失守，竟被迁徙到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">共</span>地。嘉许<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐威王\">威（齐威王）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐宣王\">宣（齐宣王）</span>能在浊世之中独尊<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>室，故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田敬仲完</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第十六。"
    },
    "85": {
      "title": "孔子世家",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>室既已衰微，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>恣意妄行。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仲尼</span>痛心<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>废<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">乐</span>崩，于是追修经术，以通达<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">王道</span>，匡救乱世、使之返于正道，他的言论文辞，为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>制立<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">仪法</span>，把<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">六经</span>的纲纪留传后世。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第十七。"
    },
    "86": {
      "title": "陈涉世家",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>失道而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周武王\">武（周武王）</span>奋起，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>室失道而<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>作。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国失政，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈涉</span>发迹起义，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>纷纷响应作难，〘※风起云蒸〙，终于倾覆<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">族</span>。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>反秦之端，从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈涉\">涉（陈涉）</span>发难而起。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈涉</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第十八。"
    },
    "87": {
      "title": "外戚世家",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋</span>高台，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：薄姬\">薄（薄姬）</span>氏在此奠基。屈意前往<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>国，其子被尊而众<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦太后\">窦（窦太后）</span>氏兴盛。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗姬</span>自恃尊贵，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王皇后\">王（王皇后）</span>氏反而得志。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈皇后\">陈（陈皇后）</span>太过骄纵，终尊<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子夫</span>为后。嘉许其德如此，故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">外戚</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第十九。"
    },
    "88": {
      "title": "楚元王世家",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>既以诡谋擒<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>；<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越荆</span>之地剽悍轻捷，于是封<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘交\">交（刘交）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>，建都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>，以加强<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮泗</span>一带，作<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>宗室屏藩。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘戊\">戊（刘戊）</span>沉溺邪谋，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘礼\">礼（刘礼）</span>得以继绍。嘉许<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘向\">游（刘向）</span>辅佐<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">祖</span>业，故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚元王</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第二十。"
    },
    "89": {
      "title": "荆燕世家",
      "text": "高祖率领师旅，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘贾</span>相助相随；被<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：黥布\">布（黥布）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">袭</span>击，丧失<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">荆</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>之地。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">营陵</span>激怒诸<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕</span>，因而王于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">琅邪</span>；受<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">午</span>怂恿而轻信<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，前往后不能归，于是西入关中，适逢<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文</span>帝，得以复王<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>地。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>未稳之际，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘贾\">贾（刘贾）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘泽\">泽（刘泽）</span>以<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">族</span>亲身份，成为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>室屏藩。故作荆燕<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第二十一。"
    },
    "90": {
      "title": "齐悼惠王世家",
      "text": "<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>已平，亲属却少；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼惠</span>年长最先封王，镇守东方土地。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">哀王</span>擅自兴兵，发怒于诸<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">驷钧</span>暴戾凶横，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">京师</span>不允。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐厉王\">厉（齐厉王）</span>内淫乱伦，祸由<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主父</span>而成。嘉许<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘肥\">肥（刘肥）</span>作为股肱辅臣，故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐悼惠王</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第二十二。"
    },
    "91": {
      "title": "萧相国世家",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>困我<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，相持<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>镇抚<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山西</span>，统筹军务、源源输送兵卒，供给粮食不断，使<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>心向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>而不愿为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧相国</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第二十三。"
    },
    "92": {
      "title": "曹相国世家",
      "text": "与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>共同平定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、拔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，终于削弱<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国。接续<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，不加变革，百姓得以安宁。嘉许<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">参（曹参）</span>不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>功、不矜能，故作曹<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第二十四。"
    },
    "93": {
      "title": "留侯世家",
      "text": "〘※运筹帷幄〙之中，决胜于无形之外，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子房</span>谋划诸事，既无显赫的声名，亦无勇猛的战功，于易处图难事、从细处成大业。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">留侯</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第二十五。"
    },
    "94": {
      "title": "陈丞相世家",
      "text": "六次奇谋既已施行，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>宾服归从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>；<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕氏</span>之变，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈平\">平（陈平）</span>为主谋，终于安定<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙</span>，保全<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社稷</span>。故作陈<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第二十六。"
    },
    "95": {
      "title": "绛侯世家",
      "text": "诸<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕</span>结党成势，图谋削弱<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">京师</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>违反常道、合于权变；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>起兵之时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">亚夫</span>屯兵<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">昌邑</span>，以扼制<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，而把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国放在敌前任其消耗。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">绛侯</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第二十七。"
    },
    "96": {
      "title": "梁孝王世家",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">七国</span>叛逆作乱，能作<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">京师</span>屏蔽者，唯<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国坚守；然而倚仗宠爱、矜夸战功，几乎招致祸患。嘉许他能够抵御<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁孝王</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第二十八。"
    },
    "97": {
      "title": "五宗世家",
      "text": "五宗同时受封为王，亲属和睦融洽，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>大小都为藩辅，各得其所，僭越拟君之事逐渐收敛。故作五宗<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第二十九。"
    },
    "98": {
      "title": "三王世家",
      "text": "三<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>受封为王，文辞有可观之处。故作<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三王</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>第三十。"
    },
    "99": {
      "title": "伯夷列传",
      "text": "末世争夺利益，唯独此二人奔向仁义；让国而饿死，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>人称颂。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯夷</span>列传第一。"
    },
    "100": {
      "title": "管晏列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晏子</span>节俭，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夷吾</span>则奢侈；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐桓公\">桓（齐桓公）</span>而称霸，因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景公</span>而得治。故作管晏列传第二。"
    },
    "101": {
      "title": "老子韩非列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李耳</span>主张<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">无为</span>自化、清净自正；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩非</span>揣度事情、循守势理。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">老子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩非</span>列传第三。"
    },
    "102": {
      "title": "司马穰苴列传",
      "text": "自古<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王者</span>都有<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">司马法</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>能够阐明发扬。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">司马</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰苴</span>列传第四。"
    },
    "103": {
      "title": "孙子吴起列传",
      "text": "非信、廉、仁、勇之人，不能传兵论<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">剑</span>，兵法与大道相通，内可修身，外可应变，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">君子</span>比附其德于此。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>列传第五。"
    },
    "104": {
      "title": "伍子胥列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：太子建\">建（太子建）</span>遭谗害，祸及<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子奢</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍尚\">尚（伍尚）</span>匡救其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>而赴死，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍员</span>出奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span>列传第六。"
    },
    "105": {
      "title": "仲尼弟子列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">孔氏</span>传述文教，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span>继起其业，都成为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">师傅</span>，崇奉仁德、砥砺大义。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仲尼</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弟子</span>列传第七。"
    },
    "106": {
      "title": "商君列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：商鞅\">鞅（商鞅）</span>离<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，能阐明其法术，使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝公</span>强盛称霸，后世遵循其法。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">商君</span>列传第八。"
    },
    "107": {
      "title": "苏秦列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>忧患连横之<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>贪得无厌，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏子</span>能保全<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，约结合从以抑制贪强。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏秦</span>列传第九。"
    },
    "108": {
      "title": "张仪列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六国</span>已合从亲善，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张仪</span>能阐明连横之说，再度使<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>之盟离散解体。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张仪</span>列传第十。"
    },
    "109": {
      "title": "樗里甘茂列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>之所以能向东雄据诸侯之上，出自<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>的谋略。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>列传第十一。"
    },
    "110": {
      "title": "穰侯列传",
      "text": "包举<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河山</span>之险，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span>，使<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>敛手而事奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，这是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏厓</span>的功劳。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰侯</span>列传第十二。"
    },
    "111": {
      "title": "白起王翦列传",
      "text": "南拔<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄢郢</span>，北摧<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长平</span>，进而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>，由<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武安</span>君统率；<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">荆</span>灭<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，出自<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>的谋划。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span>列传第十三。"
    },
    "112": {
      "title": "孟子荀卿列传",
      "text": "博采<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">儒墨</span>两家遗文，阐明<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">礼义</span>的纲纪，断绝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦惠王\">惠王（秦惠王）</span>的谋利之念，列述前代的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">兴衰</span>。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荀卿</span>列传第十四。"
    },
    "113": {
      "title": "孟尝君列传",
      "text": "好客喜<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>归附于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>，替<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>捍御<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟尝君</span>列传第十五。"
    },
    "114": {
      "title": "平原君虞卿列传",
      "text": "为争<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">冯亭</span>所献上党以权衡利害，出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国以解<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>之<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>，使自己的国君再度见重于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虞卿</span>列传第十六。"
    },
    "115": {
      "title": "魏公子列传",
      "text": "能以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">富贵</span>之身礼下<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贫贱</span>之人，以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贤能</span>之姿屈就不肖者，唯独<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">信陵君</span>能够做到。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏公子</span>列传第十七。"
    },
    "116": {
      "title": "春申君列传",
      "text": "以身殉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，终使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>太子脱离强<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，使游说之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>都南向奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，这是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄歇</span>的节义。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申君</span>列传第十八。"
    },
    "117": {
      "title": "范睢蔡泽列传",
      "text": "能忍辱于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏齐</span>，而后信威于强<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>；推贤让位，二<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>兼具之。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范睢</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡泽</span>列传第十九。"
    },
    "118": {
      "title": "乐毅列传",
      "text": "一举推行其谋略，联合五国之兵，为弱<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>报强<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>之仇，洗雪先<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>的耻辱。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>列传第二十。"
    },
    "119": {
      "title": "廉颇蔺相如列传",
      "text": "能在强<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>面前伸张己意，又在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉子</span>面前屈身示让，以此为其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>效命，都见重于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔺相如</span>列传第二十一。"
    },
    "120": {
      "title": "田单列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">湣王</span>失<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临淄</span>而奔<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">莒</span>，唯有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田单</span>凭借<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">即墨</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>走<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">骑劫</span>，保全了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社稷</span>。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田单</span>列传第二十二。"
    },
    "121": {
      "title": "鲁仲连邹阳列传",
      "text": "能用诡辩的言辞解除<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>城之患，轻视爵禄，乐于放纵己志。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲁仲连</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邹阳</span>列传第二十三。"
    },
    "122": {
      "title": "屈原贾生列传",
      "text": "以辞赋讽谏，连类取譬以争明大义，<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">离骚</span>有此精神。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">屈原</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贾生</span>列传第二十四。"
    },
    "123": {
      "title": "吕不韦列传",
      "text": "结交<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子楚</span>使之亲近，于是使<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>纷纷争相入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>效命。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>列传第二十五。"
    },
    "124": {
      "title": "刺客列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹子</span>持<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">匕首</span>，使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国收回失地，使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国申明信义；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">豫让</span>坚守大义，不怀二心。故作<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刺</span>客列传第二十六。"
    },
    "125": {
      "title": "李斯列传",
      "text": "能阐明其谋划，顺应时势助<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>并天下，终得志于海内，李斯为首谋者。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李斯</span>列传第二十七。"
    },
    "126": {
      "title": "蒙恬列传",
      "text": "替<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>开拓疆土、增广民众，北逐<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>，据河为塞，因山为固，兴筑<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">榆中</span>。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙恬</span>列传第二十八。"
    },
    "127": {
      "title": "张耳陈馀列传",
      "text": "镇守<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、扼守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">常山</span>以扩展<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河内</span>，削弱<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的权势，向<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>显明<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王的信义。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张耳</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈馀</span>列传第二十九。"
    },
    "128": {
      "title": "魏豹彭越列传",
      "text": "征收<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西河</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党</span>之兵，随军到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>；彭越侵掠<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>地以困扰<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏豹</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>列传第三十。"
    },
    "129": {
      "title": "黥布列传",
      "text": "凭借<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮南</span>叛<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>因而得<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大司马</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">殷</span>，终于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子羽</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">垓下</span>。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>列传第三十一。"
    },
    "130": {
      "title": "淮阴侯列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军迫逼我于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">京索</span>之间，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>攻拔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，平定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>据有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>三分之二，以此消灭<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">淮阴侯</span>列传第三十二。"
    },
    "131": {
      "title": "韩信卢绾列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>相持于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巩洛</span>之间，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>镇守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">颍川</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>切断<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项籍\">籍（项籍）</span>的粮道。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>列传第三十三。"
    },
    "132": {
      "title": "田儋列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>背叛<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>，唯<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>牵制<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子羽</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">城阳</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>得以乘间攻入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田儋</span>列传第三十四。"
    },
    "133": {
      "title": "樊郦列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>城野<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>，有功归报，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：樊哙\">哙（樊哙）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郦商\">商（郦商）</span>均有出力，不仅仅执<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">鞭</span>鞭策军前，又曾助高祖脱难。故作樊郦列传第三十五。"
    },
    "134": {
      "title": "张丞相列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝初定，典章制度尚未明备，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张苍\">苍（张苍）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">主计</span>，整齐度量衡，次序<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">律历</span>。故作张<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>列传第三十六。"
    },
    "135": {
      "title": "郦生陆贾列传",
      "text": "缔结言辞、通使四方，约结归附<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>；<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>皆亲附，归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>成为屏藩。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦生</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陆贾</span>列传第三十七。"
    },
    "136": {
      "title": "傅靳蒯成列传",
      "text": "欲详知<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>之事，唯<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周緤</span>常从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>，平定<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。故作傅靳<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒯成</span>列传第三十八。"
    },
    "137": {
      "title": "刘敬叔孙通列传",
      "text": "迁徙豪强<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">族</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>建都，与<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>约和；申明朝廷之礼，次定<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">仪法</span>。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘敬</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>列传第三十九。"
    },
    "138": {
      "title": "季布栾布列传",
      "text": "能够屈刚为柔，终成为列位之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栾公</span>不慑于威势而冒死报故主。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栾布</span>列传第四十。"
    },
    "139": {
      "title": "袁盎晁错列传",
      "text": "敢于犯颜直谏以通达主上的大义，不顾自身安危，为国家树立长远谋画。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁盎</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晁错</span>列传第四十一。"
    },
    "140": {
      "title": "张释之冯唐列传",
      "text": "守法而不失<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大理</span>之职，称述古代贤人，以增长主上的英明。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张释之</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯唐</span>列传第四十二。"
    },
    "141": {
      "title": "万石张叔列传",
      "text": "敦厚仁慈孝顺，〘※讷於言，敏於行|讷言敏行〙，务在谨慎恭敬，是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">君子</span>长者。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">万石</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张叔</span>列传第四十三。"
    },
    "142": {
      "title": "田叔列传",
      "text": "守节正直，其义足以令人称廉，其行足以砥砺贤人，身任重权而不为非理所屈挠。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田叔</span>列传第四十四。"
    },
    "143": {
      "title": "扁鹊仓公列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">扁鹊</span>谈论医道，为方术者所宗，守数精明；后世相传，不能更易，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仓公</span>可说是接近他的水平了。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">扁鹊</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仓公</span>列传第四十五。"
    },
    "144": {
      "title": "吴王濞列传",
      "text": "由于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘仲\">仲（刘仲）</span>被省免王位，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘濞\">濞（刘濞）</span>得以王<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>，适逢<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝初定，以此镇抚<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江淮</span>之间。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴王濞</span>列传第四十六。"
    },
    "145": {
      "title": "魏其武安列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>作乱，宗亲中唯<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦婴\">婴（窦婴）</span>贤明而喜<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>向往归附，率军抗敌于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏其</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武安</span>列传第四十七。"
    },
    "146": {
      "title": "韩长孺列传",
      "text": "智慧足以应付近世的变化，宽厚足以得人之心。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩长孺</span>列传第四十八。"
    },
    "147": {
      "title": "李将军列传",
      "text": "临敌勇猛，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">仁爱</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒，号令简明，军队乐于归附。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李将军</span>列传第四十九。"
    },
    "148": {
      "title": "匈奴列传",
      "text": "自<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三代</span>以来，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>常成为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>的边患；欲知强弱的时势、设立防备征讨之策，故作<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>列传第五十。"
    },
    "149": {
      "title": "卫将军骠骑列传",
      "text": "打通曲塞，开广<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河南</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">祁连</span>，开通西域诸国，使北<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>披靡。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫将军</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骠骑</span>列传第五十一。"
    },
    "150": {
      "title": "平津侯列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宗室</span>以侈靡相夸耀，唯独<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙弘\">弘（公孙弘）</span>节衣缩食为百官表率。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平津侯</span>列传第五十二。"
    },
    "151": {
      "title": "南越列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>既已平定<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵佗\">佗（赵佗）</span>能够安集<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">杨越</span>以守南方屏藩，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">纳贡</span>效职。故作<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南越</span>列传第五十三。"
    },
    "152": {
      "title": "东越列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王叛逆，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">瓯</span>人<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘濞\">濞（刘濞）</span>，保守封禺之地称<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>。故作<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东越</span>列传第五十四。"
    },
    "153": {
      "title": "朝鲜列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕丹</span>之乱散于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">辽间</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫满\">满（卫满）</span>收抚这些逃亡之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>，聚于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海东</span>，安集真藩，守塞为外<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">朝鲜</span>列传第五十五。"
    },
    "154": {
      "title": "西南夷列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">唐蒙</span>出使略通<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">夜郎</span>，而<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">邛笮</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>请求归为内<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>、受汉朝派官吏。故作<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">西南夷</span>列传第五十六。"
    },
    "155": {
      "title": "司马相如列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">子虚</span>之事，<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">大人赋</span>之说，词藻靡丽多有夸饰，然而其旨归在于风谏，最终归向<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">无为</span>。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">司马相如</span>列传第五十七。"
    },
    "156": {
      "title": "淮南衡山列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>叛逆被诛，其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘长\">长（刘长）</span>继承其国，以镇抚<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江淮</span>之南，安定剽悍的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>地庶<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">淮南</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">衡山</span>列传第五十八。"
    },
    "157": {
      "title": "循吏列传",
      "text": "奉公守法、循理治事之吏，不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>功、不矜能，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>无所称颂，也无过失之行。故作循吏列传第五十九。"
    },
    "158": {
      "title": "汲郑列传",
      "text": "端正<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣冠</span>立于朝廷，使<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>莫敢妄发浮夸之言，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汲黯\">长孺（汲黯）</span>庄重严正；喜欢举荐他人、称道长者，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郑当时\">壮（郑当时）</span>有此美德。故作汲郑列传第六十。"
    },
    "159": {
      "title": "儒林列传",
      "text": "自<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>去世之后，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">京师</span>很少有尊崇学校的，唯有<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">建元</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元狩</span>年间，文教粲然兴盛。故作儒林列传第六十一。"
    },
    "160": {
      "title": "酷吏列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>背弃本业、多尚机巧，奸邪违法，善人不能感化，唯有一切严峻削刻才能整齐。故作酷吏列传第六十二。"
    },
    "161": {
      "title": "大宛列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>既已通使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">大夏</span>，而<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西极</span>远方的蛮夷，都引领内向，想要观瞻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>。故作<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">大宛</span>列传第六十三。"
    },
    "162": {
      "title": "游侠列传",
      "text": "救人于困厄，振济匮乏之人，仁者有之；既不失信于人，又不背弃诺言，义者有可<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>之处。故作<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">游侠</span>列传第六十四。"
    },
    "163": {
      "title": "佞幸列传",
      "text": "侍奉人<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>能使君主耳目愉悦、颜色和顺，从而得到亲近，不仅靠美色取爱，才能也各有所长。故作佞幸列传第六十五。"
    },
    "164": {
      "title": "滑稽列传",
      "text": "不随流俗，不争势利，上下无所滞碍，无人能加害，以道为用。故作滑稽列传第六十六。"
    },
    "165": {
      "title": "日者列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>各有占日者，各有其地习用之术。欲概略考察其大要，故作日者列传第六十七。"
    },
    "166": {
      "title": "龟策列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三王</span>使用不同的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">龟</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">四夷</span>各有各的卜法，然而都用以决断<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">吉凶</span>。略窥其要旨，故作龟策列传第六十八。"
    },
    "167": {
      "title": "货殖列传",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">布衣</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">匹夫</span>之人，不妨害政事，不妨碍<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>，按时<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>与而生息财富，智者有可采择之处。故作货殖列传第六十九。"
    },
    "168": {
      "title": "全书总结·汉兴复古",
      "text": "我<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝承接<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">五帝</span>的余绪，续承<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三代</span>的事业。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>道衰废，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>废除古文，焚毁<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">诗书</span>，因此<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">明堂</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">石室金匮玉版</span>所藏的图书典籍散乱遗失。及至<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝兴起，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>制定<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">律令</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>申明<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">军法</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张苍</span>创立<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">章程</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>制定<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼仪</span>，于是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">文学</span>之士彬彬日盛，<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">诗书</span>之籍也陆续出现。"
    },
    "169": {
      "title": "百年遗文尽集太史公",
      "text": "自从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹参</span>举荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">盖公</span>倡言<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">黄老</span>之学，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">贾生</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晁错</span>阐明<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">申</span>、<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">商</span>之术，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙弘</span>以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">儒</span>术显达，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">百年</span>之间，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的遗文古事无不汇集到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：司马迁\">太史公（司马迁）</span>之手。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：司马迁\">太史公（司马迁）</span>继承<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父子</span>相续之职业。说：\"啊！我想到先人曾经掌管此事，显扬于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">唐虞</span>之际，到了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>朝又续典其事，所以<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">司马氏</span>世代主掌<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">天官</span>之职。到了我身上，当敬谨从事啊！当敬谨从事啊！\""
    },
    "170": {
      "title": "网罗放失旧闻·十二本纪十表八书",
      "text": "网罗搜集<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>散失的旧闻，考察王业兴起之源，探索其始、察其终局，观其盛、察其衰，论述考订史实，约略推及<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三代</span>，详记<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，上起<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">轩辕</span>，下至当今，著十二<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">本纪</span>，已经分条列目了。又因时代交错、年代有差难明，作十表。<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼乐</span>的损益，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">律历</span>的改革，兵权、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山川</span>、<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">鬼神</span>、<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">天</span>人之际的学问、承继衰敝、通达变革之道，作八书。"
    },
    "171": {
      "title": "三十世家七十列传·一家之言",
      "text": "<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">二十八宿</span>环绕<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">北辰</span>，三十条辐辏共于一毂，运行无穷，配以辅弼股肱之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，忠信地奉行其道，以侍奉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">主上</span>，作三十<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">世家</span>。扶持道义、卓异不凡，不使自己失去时机，立功名于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，作七十列传。共一百三十篇，五十二万六千五百字，是为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：司马迁\">太史公（司马迁）</span>之书。这是序目大略，用以拾遗补阙，成〘※一家之言〙，协和<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">六经</span>的异传，整理<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">百家</span>的杂说，藏之于名<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山</span>，副本留在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">京师</span>，以待后世<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">圣人</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">君子</span>观览。此为第七十。"
    },
    "172": {
      "title": "后人赞辞",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太史</span>公才学俊良，确实能纂集先人之德业。 周游四方历览天下，东西南北无所不至。 事迹核实而文辞简练，足以称为\"实录\"。 回复<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任安\">任（任安）</span>的来书，为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李陵\">李（李陵）</span>之事申辩而致<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">下狱</span>。 可惜原书有所残缺，无才之人不可妄加续补！ :::"
    }
  }
}